TextArea_SetText
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<TextGadgets=>textgadgets/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_set_text>
Syntax:	TextArea_SetText
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 2 (16410)
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = text
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method replaces all text displayed in a text area. The replacement string in the buffer at R4 must be zero terminated and may contain line feeds.